summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Twentieth Avenue Northeast from East Fiftieth Street to East Fifty-eighth Street et al, in the City of Seattle, by grading and under Ordinance No. 24846, creating Local Improvement District No. 2386 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
